MID_支援_ハロルド_ベルカ_Ｃ: $t1$Wmベルカ|7$Wmハロルド|3$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|$w0|Belka, my friend.$k$pI saw you speaking to some shady\nindividuals just now. Who were they?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa…………$k$p$Eキメ,|...That's none of your business.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaBut those men reeked\nwith the stench of evil.$k$p$Eキメ,|Mingling with those sorts\nwon't bring you any good.$k$pIt's a stain upon the honor of\nyour master, Lady Camilla.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|…………$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|You don't want to talk?\nVery well.$k$p$Eキメ,|However, I'll be watching you\nwith the eyes of justice.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,|Justice, you say...?$k$pWhat is justice?\nI don't know...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,|So you are interested in justice?\nI shall tell you, then.$k$p$E通常,|First, to wake up before others\nto patrol the streets.$k$p$E怒,|If you see a lost child, you must search\nhigh and low for their parents.$k$p$E苦,汗|If you see a tired old man, you must\ntake him on your back and be his legs.$k$pIf you see a crying baby,\ncry with it until it smiles again.$k$p$E怒,|When you see a fight, intervene and turn\ntheir clashing fists into a shake of hands.$k$p$Eキメ,|That is what my justice is.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa…………$k$p$E通常,|You are intriguing.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,|Intriguing?\nOho...$k$p$E通常2,|If this interests you, I can\ntell you more. Let's see...$k
MID_支援_ハロルド_ベルカ_Ｂ: $t1$Wmベルカ|7$Wmハロルド|3$w0|$Wsハロルド|$WaHow was it, Belka? Have I deepened\nyour understanding of justice?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$WaYes... I think I've come to understand a\nlittle of what your brand of justice is...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,|Oh, really?\nThat pleases me.$k$pI didn't think you would listen so much.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|...I have never had an upbringing.$k$pPerhaps that is why I don't have\nan idea of what is just or unjust.$k$pThat may be why I was\ninterested to hear more.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|...Is that so?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|...It's almost time.\nI'm going.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|Going where?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,|I can't tell you.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|It wouldn't have anything to do\nwith those shady men, would it?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|...Yes, it does. I have been asked\nto assassinate a certain man.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,汗|Assassinate?\nWho is your target?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$WaA government official\nin the royal capital.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|I see. That's quite the coincidence.$k$pI've taken up a request as well.$k$pA request to guard a government\nofficial in the royal capital. $k$pWord is that they are on guard after\ndiscovering plots to assassinate them.$k$pThus, I'll have to go.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E苦,汗|Huh? Then...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|Yes, it is as you suspect.\nIt is a pity, but...$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa…………$k$p$E怒,|Just for your information, I will do my\njob regardless of any circumstances.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|Is that so? What a coincidence.\nThe same goes for me.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|...I see.$k
MID_支援_ハロルド_ベルカ_Ａ: $t1$Wmベルカ|7$Wmハロルド|3$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|$w0|About the affair with the officials, Belka,\nwhy did you retire partway through?$k$p$E怒,|I thought you claimed to do your job\nregardless of the circumstances.$k$p$E怒,汗|I can't believe you'd pull back for me...$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|That is just your misunderstanding...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|Then why...?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,|...I believed there was a third party.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|A third party?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E苦,汗|Yes. There was another assassin there.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|Hm? Was there really?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|Yes, I'll tell you.$k$pI was hiding a short distance away from\nthe building, watching my mark, and$k$pwaiting for a chance to kill him when the\ntarget that you were escorting arrived.$k$p$E怒,|The next moment... a horse wagon\ncame through and sent you flying.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|Yeah, that did happen.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E苦,汗|But that wasn't all. Next, the\nceiling collapsed on top of you.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,汗|Right, that happened too.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|That could only have been the\nwork of a skilled assassin...$k$p$E怒,汗|However, I don't know what he was after.$k$pThat's why I decided to retreat\nand wait for my next chance.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|…………$k$pUm, about that...$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|Do you know something?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常2,汗|No, nothing at all.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|...To be honest, that was a relief.$k$pIf I had continued with my mission,\nI may have had to kill you.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|So you're happy that I'm alive?$k$pThat doesn't sound like\nsomething an assassin would say.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|No, it's not.$k$pBut I wanted to hear you speak\nmore of justice... That is the truth.$k$p$E怒,|I always suspected people who acted\nunder the pretenses of justice,$k$pand thought them all to be frauds.$k$pHowever, you are different.$k$p$Eキメ,|This may be rude, but it's\nbecause you are an idiot.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|An idiot?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|Yes. You idiotically live your life with\na single-minded adherence to justice.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,|Hahaha, that's an honor.\nI'll take it as a compliment.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E笑,|I would like to hear more someday.$k
MID_支援_ハロルド_ベルカ_Ｓ: $t1$Wmベルカ|7$Wmハロルド|3$w0|$Wsベルカ|$WaHarold, you're here...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaBelka, I've been waiting for you.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,|...Why?\nWhat are you doing out here...?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaWhat I want to discuss today is...$k$p$E苦,汗|Uwaaaaah!!$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wd$w0|$w200|$SspSE_EVT_BODYFALL|$w800|$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E苦,汗|!?\nWhy is there a pitfall here!?$k$pCould it be?\nThe assassin from before!?$k$pKh, so he was after you all along!$k$p$E怒,|Harold, give me your hand...$k\n$Wmハロルド|3$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|$w0|Th-thanks...\nI owe you one.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E苦,汗|Let's move...\nIt's dangerous to remain here...$k\n$Wc$Sbv40|1000|$Fo1000|$Wsベルカ|$Wd$Wsハロルド|$Wd$w0|$Sbv100|1000|$Fi1000|$Wmベルカ|7$Wmハロルド|3$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|$w0|That was a close call...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaYeah... so, before anything\nelse happens, take this.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E苦,汗|I-is this...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,照|Yes, it's a ring.\nI wanted to propose to you.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E苦,照|N-no... wait...\nI need time to take the situation in...$k$p$E怒,照|It's true that when I'm with you I...\nI...$k$pBut, marriage...requires love...$k$p$E苦,照|And I... do not know much of it.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,照|...I'm a meddlesome man.$k$p$E通常,照|If you do not understand love, then I\nshall tell you about it until you do.$k$p$Eキメ,照|I want to discuss love with you,\nexpress it to you,$k$pand spend twenty-four hours of\neach day teaching you about it.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,照|…………$k$p$E通常,照|Do you?\nAll right.$k$p$Eキメ,照|Then in exchange for teaching me about\nlove, I'll kill the assassin targeting you.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,照|…………$k$pBelka, about that...$k$p$E怒,汗|That was no assassin.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E苦,汗|Huh?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|The truth is, I just have extraordinarily\nbad luck. Those were all coincidences.$k$pThere was no third party, and that\nassassin never existed in the first place.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|…………$k$p…………$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,汗|B-Belka?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E笑2,|Hahaha... Ahahaha.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,汗|Wh-what's the matter!?\nI've never seen you laugh like this before!$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E笑,|Haha... Sorry...$k$pI found it funny that someone of my caliber\nwould be fooled by a nonexistent assassin...$k$p$E笑2,|But, I'm grateful for your misfortune.$k$pIf it weren't for that...\nwe would not be so close.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,照|That's right... And I would have never\nseen you smile like this, either.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E笑,照|...Yes. If we're together, then your\nmisfortune won't be such a bad thing.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,照|Thank you...\nNow, Belka, take this ring.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$WaYes, with pleasure.$k
